Optional Features
-----------------

M.2 NVMe Module
***************

The product has a |m2_desc| slot for a NVMe SSD, M.2 SSD is optional and can be selected when placing an order.

|Product| does not include the NVMe SSD by default.

**Important note**: |m2_4g_conflict|.

4G/LTE Module
*************

The product has a Mini-PCIe slot, you can install a 3G/4G/LTE/GPS module to it if you need 3G/4G/LTE/GPS.

|Product| does not include the 3G/4G/LTE/GPS module by default. This module is optional and can be selected at the Chipsee store during the ordering process.

**Important note**: |m2_4g_conflict|.

RS232/RS485/CAN/Relay
*********************

The product's RS232/RS485/CAN/Relay can be configured in the factory, these options are supported:

* 2 x RS232, 1 x RS485, 0 x CAN, 1 x Relay **(default)**
* 1 x RS232, 2 x RS485, 0 x CAN, 1 x Relay
* 1 x RS232, 1 x RS485, 1 x CAN, 1 x Relay
* 2 x RS232, 1 x RS485, 1 x CAN, 0 x Relay

Please contact us if you need option 2,3 or 4.

.. warning::   

   | Installation, repair, and maintenance tasks should be performed by trained personnel only.
   | Chipsee does not bear any responsibility for damage caused by inadequate handling of the product.

